item.title: Comment on Wide round accent table by Linethemes
item.dc:creator: Linethemes
item.description: Good workmanship, very nice quality. This end table looks great in living room. I just wish it was 1 inch wider in diameter & at least 3 inches taller. Nonetheless, it’s still a beautiful accent table that has a timeless look.
